WEBVTT

00:00:29.297 --> 00:00:30.604
To se zove hrabrost.

00:00:31.336 --> 00:00:32.598
I baš kao strah,

00:00:33.069 --> 00:00:34.848
hrabrost je prelazna.

00:00:35.848 --> 00:00:38.150
Ja sam iz Istočnog St. Luisa, Ilinois.

00:00:38.150 --> 00:00:39.333
To je malen grad

00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:42.152
nasuprot rijeke Misisipi
od St. Luisa, Misuri.

00:00:42.152 --> 00:00:45.855
Ja sam čitav život živio
u St. Luisu i okolici.

00:00:48.448 --> 00:00:49.791
Kada je Majkl Braun džunior,

00:00:49.791 --> 00:00:51.055
prosječan tinejdžer,

00:00:51.055 --> 00:00:54.697
upucan od strane policije 2014-e
u Fergusonu, Misuri,

00:00:55.621 --> 00:00:58.381
predgrađu sjeverno od Sent Luisa,

00:00:58.925 --> 00:01:00.724
sjećam se da sam pomislio,